Class StudyGroupCollectionManager

java.lang.Object
Server.collectionManagers.StudyGroupCollectionManager
public class StudyGroupCollectionManager extends Object
Class that manages the collection of StudyGroup objects. Provides methods for adding, removing, and manipulating the collection.
